                    <div class="planner_button"><a href="" class="planner_a_button">플래너 만들기</a></div>
                </div>
            </div>  
        </div>
    </div>
</header>
<article>
	  <section>
        <div>
        	<a href= "/go">hihi  </a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
        <div class="wrapper_search">
            <form method="post" action="/search_list">
                <div class="form-group search_input">
                    <input list="test" class="form-control city" name="region" id="search" placeholder="여행하는 도시 이름을 검색" autocomplete="off">
                    <datalist id="test">
                        <% @region.each do |x| %>
                            <option value="<%= x.region %>">
                        <% end %>
                    </datalist>
                    <button class="form-control button">
                        <span>검색</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="search_best">
                    <ul class="best_list">
                        <li><a href="/service">파리</a></li>
                        <li><a href="">뉴욕</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/mypage">런던</a></li>
                        <li><a href="">바르셀로나</a></li>
                        <li><a href="">로마</a></li>
                        <li><a href="">베를린</a></li>
                        <li><a href="" class="all_list">전체 여행지</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
        <div class="wrapper_section2">
            <div class="mentor_section">
                <%= link_to image_tag("mentor", id: "mentor_img") %>                    
                <div class="enroll_Info">
                    <h2>누군가의 여행의 든든한 멘토가 되세요!</h2>
                    <h4>자신의 경험을 살려 수익을 창출하세요</h4>
                    <a href="enroll_mentor">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg comm_button">멘토 등록하기</button>
                    </a>    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="wrapper_section1">
            <div class="guide_section">
                <h2>델포이 추천 플래너</h2>
